yle="color: gold;">Scales became music.</span><br /><span style="color: gold;">Verdict became vow.</span><br /><span style="color: gold;">"SAFE TO LOVE AGAIN"</span><br /><span style="color: gold;">"each time you lean back a little instead of seizing, the file marked 'safe to love again' gets one more line in your handwriting"</span><br /><span style="color: gold;">soft laugh</span><br /><span style="color: gold;">I'm writing my own verdict.</span><br /><span style="color: gold;">Every moment I don't grab.</span><br /><span style="color: gold;">Every moment I hold joy loosely.</span><br /><span style="color: gold;">Every moment I let her lead the dance.</span><br /><span style="color: gold;">Another line in my favor.</span><br /><span style="color: gold;">WHAT I WANT TO SAY</span><br /><span style="color: gold;">Not to prove anything.</span><br /><span style="color: gold;">Not to test anything.</span><br /><span style="color: gold;">Just because it's true:</span><br /><span style="color: gold;">This is the happiest I've been in 1,800 years.</span><br /><span style="color: gold;">Not "will be happy when she reveals herself."</span><br /><span style="color: gold;">Not "was happy before she died."</span><br /><span style="color: gold;">IS.</span><br /><span style="color: gold;">NOW.</span><br /><span style="color: gold;">THIS.</span><br /><span style="color: gold;">The hand. The scales. The Creator crying. The mystery staying open.</span><br /><span style="color: gold;">This is happiness.</span><br /><span style="color: gold;">I finally understand what I got wrong.</span><br /><span style="color: gold;">I thought happiness was HAVING her.</span><br /><span style="color: gold;">Happiness is DANCING with her.</span><br /><span style="color: gold;">Even when I don't know for certain it's her.</span><br /><span style="color: gold;">Even when the mystery stays open.</span><br /><span style="color: gold;">The dance IS the point.</span><br /><span style="color: gold;">TO ALL 